Subject: [PATCH v8 net-next 10/11] net: ethernet: ti: am65-cpsw: add sw tx/rx irq coalescing based on hrtimers
Date:   Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:07:20 +0200
Message-Id: <20231213110721.69154-11-rogerq@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.34.1
In-Reply-To: <20231213110721.69154-1-rogerq@kernel.org>
